# Static archive of GameCon 2004 (reconstructed from the Internet Archive).
#
# The 2004 festival ran 8.-11. 7. 2004 in OLOMOUC (DDM, tř. 17. listopadu 47 +
# nearby university dorms). It was run by the Altar publishing house, and in
# 2004 GameCon was a SECTION of the whole altar.cz publisher site (path
# altar.cz/gamecon/) — the same path-era as 2005, older than the
# gamecon.altar.cz subdomain (2006-2008).
#
# Scope: only the GameCon pages were reconstructed (~31 /gamecon/ pages, incl.
# the Mistrovství v DrD results archive vysledky95..vysledky04), served here at
# the root; the original /gamecon/ link prefix was rewritten to /. Pages were
# restored from web.archive.org, transcoded WINDOWS-1250 -> UTF-8 (with an
# injected <meta charset>, since the source declared charset only via the HTTP
# header).
#
# The pages share Altar's global site nav, which links all over the parent
# publisher site (/altar/*, /drd/, /kontakt/, /cgi/*, the shop, …). Those
# cross-site links are intentionally NOT reconstructed — they fall to the themed
# 404, as does any uncaptured URL. Assets (stylesheets/default.css,
# img/gamecon/*) are served at their original absolute paths.

DirectoryIndex index.html
ErrorDocument 404 /404.html

<IfModule mod_rewrite.c>
    RewriteEngine On

    # Serve real files / dirs directly (pages at root, assets under their paths).
    RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} -f [OR]
    RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} -d
    RewriteRule ^ - [L]

    # Homepage.
    RewriteRule ^$  index.html [L]

    # Everything else (cross-site Altar chrome, uncaptured) -> themed 404.
    RewriteRule ^.*$ - [R=404,L]
</IfModule>
